Third-party software this plugin links against / invokes at runtime
---------------------------------------------------------------------

The MCP server (`servers/openvpn3/openvpn3_mcp/`) and the Stop/SessionEnd
teardown hook (`hooks/scripts/teardown.py`) import and call into the
`openvpn3` Python module shipped with the `openvpn3-client` system package:

    OpenVPN 3 Linux client
    https://github.com/OpenVPN/openvpn3-linux
    https://codeberg.org/OpenVPN/openvpn3-linux
    License: AGPL-3.0-only
    Copyright (C) 2017-2023 OpenVPN Inc <sales@openvpn.net>
    Copyright (C) 2017-2023 David Sommerseth <davids@openvpn.net>

The installed copy on your system is typically at:

    /usr/lib/python3/dist-packages/openvpn3/

The plugin also depends on `dbus-python` (`python3-dbus`) for D-Bus access:

    dbus-python
    https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/dbus/dbus-python
    License: AFL-2.1 OR GPL-2.0-or-later

